@startuml Sequence_UC08
title UC-08: Kelola Produksi

actor "Bagian Produksi" as User
participant "Halaman Produksi\n(livewire/production)" as View
participant "Production\\AntrianProduksi\n(Livewire)" as AntrianComponent
participant "Production\\Mulai\n(Livewire)" as MulaiComponent
participant "Production Model" as ProductionModel
participant "ProductionDetail Model" as DetailModel
participant "MaterialDetail Model" as MatDetailModel
participant "Notification Model" as NotifModel
database "Database" as DB

== Lihat Antrian Produksi ==
User -> View: Membuka /produksi/antrian
View -> AntrianComponent: mount()
AntrianComponent -> DB: SELECT productions JOIN transactions\nWHERE status = 'Menunggu'\nAND method != 'siap_beli'
DB --> AntrianComponent: Daftar antrian pesanan
AntrianComponent --> View: Render antrian produksi

== Mulai Produksi Pesanan ==
User -> View: Klik Mulai Produksi pada pesanan
View -> MulaiComponent: mount($productionId)
MulaiComponent -> ProductionModel: Production::findOrFail($id)->load(['details.product'])
ProductionModel -> DB: SELECT productions, production_details
DB --> MulaiComponent: Data produksi

User -> View: Isi jumlah hasil produksi lalu simpan
View -> MulaiComponent: save()
MulaiComponent -> MulaiComponent: Cek ketersediaan stok tiap bahan

alt Stok bahan tidak mencukupi
  MulaiComponent --> View: Pesan error bahan kurang
else Stok mencukupi
  loop Setiap bahan dalam komposisi
    MulaiComponent -> MatDetailModel: Kurangi supply_quantity
    MatDetailModel -> DB: UPDATE material_details
  end
  MulaiComponent -> DetailModel: ProductionDetail::update(['quantity_get'=>...])
  DetailModel -> DB: UPDATE production_details
  MulaiComponent -> ProductionModel: $production->update(['status'=>'Selesai'])
  ProductionModel -> DB: UPDATE productions
  MulaiComponent -> DB: UPDATE transactions SET status = 'Dapat Diambil'
  MulaiComponent -> NotifModel: Notification::create(['type'=>'production_done',...])
  NotifModel -> DB: INSERT INTO notifications
  MulaiComponent --> View: Notifikasi sukses → redirect daftar
end

== Produksi Siap Beli ==
User -> View: Klik Tambah Produksi Siap Beli
View -> MulaiComponent: mountReadyToBuy()
User -> View: Isi produk & jumlah rencana lalu simpan
View -> MulaiComponent: saveReadyToBuy()

MulaiComponent -> MulaiComponent: Cek stok bahan
alt Stok tidak cukup
  MulaiComponent --> View: Pesan error bahan kurang
else Cukup
  MulaiComponent -> ProductionModel: Production::create(['method'=>'siap_beli',...])
  ProductionModel -> DB: INSERT INTO productions
  MulaiComponent -> DetailModel: ProductionDetail::insert([...])
  DetailModel -> DB: INSERT INTO production_details
  MulaiComponent --> View: Notifikasi sukses
end

User -> View: Klik Selesaikan Produksi Siap Beli
View -> MulaiComponent: finish()
MulaiComponent -> DB: UPDATE products SET stock = stock + quantity_get
MulaiComponent -> ProductionModel: $production->update(['status'=>'Selesai'])
MulaiComponent --> View: Notifikasi sukses

@enduml
